des:
No one tells jokes quite like a dad. They can be hilarious or painfully cringe-worthy. It doesn't matter to a dad. He tells them regardless.
The World's Best Dad Jokes contains hundreds of dad jokes. Use them yourself or just bring back memories of the time when your dad told them.
If you have an Echo Show, Echo Spot or Kindle you can read the jokes on the screen
